column5: Nice salmon mike !!!   well done,they look great,and i bet they taste even better!!...thanks for the tease,show us some more fish-porn please.  ....cheers
WOW,  as usual I am unbelieveably jealous.  I caught a an old boot in the oshawa creek this week...it was brown...ish and kinda smelly.  I bet youre jealous.  ya, i knew you would be
Shopping cart boots ..... dirtiest boots of the east LOL

jdmls,  some bugger pulled out my favourite fish holding shopping cart!  can usually find 2 or 3 nice steelies sitting in behind there, feeding on the rice grains that are falling out of the no frills bag just upstream.  I think they bite easily because they are a little drunk from those empty beer cans that are stuck under the rusty car hood.   Oh what I would give to fish in alaska, Solo I bet you didnt see one shopping cart the whole time!
I bet those ho's gave your soul an orgasmic experience  Can't wait for the full report!
ah.    like a little old lady, eh?   Nice.  so wadda ya figure?   August?
